important.para:
Regardless of the current target, do not rely on
:latest for reproducible builds. Always pin to an
explicit version tag (for example 15.7 for &slsa;
15 SP7, or the relevant 16.x tag for &suselinux;
16) in your FROM lines, in your CI pipelines and
in any podman pull command, so that a future
:latest pivot does not silently change the base of
your deployment. &slsa; 15 SP7 &bcia;s remain maintained until the
end of general support for SP7 (31 July 2031). For SP6 and earlier,
refer to .
